---
// Real business scenarios FDEs solve
---

<section id="business-impact" class="py-16">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">💰 Real Business Impact</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">How FDEs translate code into revenue, savings, and risk reduction</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Key Insight -->
  <div class="mb-12 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500/10 to-orange-500/10 border border-amber-500/20">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <span class="text-4xl">💡</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">FDE = Engineer who translates code into duit</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">Junior tanya "kenapa pakai React?" — Senior tanya "kenapa pakai DB ini?" — <strong class="text-amber-400">FDE tanya "kenapa customer mau bayar $500K/tahun?"</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scenario Cards -->
  <div class="space-y-8">
    
    <!-- Scenario 1: Manual → Automation -->
    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-2xl">⚙️</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Scenario 1: Manual Process → Automation</h3>
        <span class="ml-auto text-xs bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-2 py-1 rounded">OPEX SAVINGS</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">😤 Customer Complaint</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm italic">"Tim gue spend 4 jam/hari copy-paste data dari email ke spreadsheet ke sistem lain"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">🔍 FDE Analysis</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• 4h/day × 5 days × 52 weeks = 1,040 hrs/year</li>
            <li>• Hourly cost: $25</li>
            <li>• Annual: $26K per person</li>
            <li>• 10 people: <strong>$260,000/year</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">💰 Solution Impact</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Build cost: $40K (2 months)</li>
            <li>• Annual savings: $260K</li>
            <li>• ROI: <strong class="text-green-400">6.5x in Year 1</strong></li>
            <li>• Payback: 2 months</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 mb-2">🗣️ How to present this:</h4>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
          <div><span class="text-indigo-400">To CFO:</span> <span class="text-slate-300">"ROI 6.5x. Bayar balik 2 bulan."</span></div>
          <div><span class="text-indigo-400">To VP:</span> <span class="text-slate-300">"10 orang fokus ke higher-value work."</span></div>
          <div><span class="text-indigo-400">To Users:</span> <span class="text-slate-300">"Copy-paste hilang. Data auto-ada."</span></div>
          <div><span class="text-indigo-400">To IT:</span> <span class="text-slate-300">"Audit trail lengkap. Error turun 95%."</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scenario 2: Churn → MRR Growth -->
    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-2xl">📈</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Scenario 2: Churn Prevention → MRR Growth</h3>
        <span class="ml-auto text-xs bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 px-2 py-1 rounded">REVENUE</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">😤 Customer Complaint</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm italic">"Customer sering complain error di checkout. Banyak abandoned cart."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">🔍 FDE Analysis</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• 1,000 checkouts/day</li>
            <li>• 15% abandonment = 150 lost/day</li>
            <li>• Average order: $50</li>
            <li>• Lost: <strong>$2.7M/year</strong></li>
            <li>• Root cause: 60% timeout, 25% UX</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">💰 Solution Impact</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Build cost: $60K</li>
            <li>• Recovered: 100 orders/day</li>
            <li>• Revenue: <strong class="text-green-400">$1.8M/year</strong></li>
            <li>• ROI: <strong class="text-green-400">30x</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scenario 3: AWS Cost Optimization -->
    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-2xl">☁️</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Scenario 3: AWS Cost Optimization → OpEx Reduction</h3>
        <span class="ml-auto text-xs bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 px-2 py-1 rounded">OPEX</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">😤 Customer Complaint</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm italic">"Server cost naik terus. CFO minta cut 30%."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">🔍 FDE Analysis</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• AWS bill: $50K/month</li>
            <li>• Peak: 4 hours/day</li>
            <li>• Off-peak: 80% idle</li>
            <li>• Waste: <strong>$17.5K/month</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">💰 Solution Impact</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Right-size + auto-scale</li>
            <li>• Reserved instances: -30%</li>
            <li>• CDN: reduce compute</li>
            <li>• Savings: <strong class="text-green-400">$210K/year</strong></li>
            <li>• Build cost: $30K (2 weeks)</li>
            <li>• ROI: <strong class="text-green-400">7x</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scenario 4: Compliance → Deal Enablement -->
    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-2xl">🇪🇺</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Scenario 4: GDPR Compliance → Deal Enablement</h3>
        <span class="ml-auto text-xs bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-2 py-1 rounded">RISK + REVENUE</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">😤 Customer Situation</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm italic">"Kita mau masuk EU market. Butuh GDPR compliant dalam 3 bulan atau deal $2M batal."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">🔍 FDE Scope</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Data inventory & mapping</li>
            <li>• Consent management</li>
            <li>• Right to erasure (delete data)</li>
            <li>• Data export (portability)</li>
            <li>• Audit logging</li>
            <li>• Security headers (CSP, HSTS)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">💰 Business Value</h4>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Enable <strong class="text-green-400">$2M deal</strong></li>
            <li>• Avoid <strong class="text-red-400">€800K fine</strong> (4% of €20M)</li>
            <li>• Open EU: <strong class="text-green-400">$5M+ potential</strong></li>
            <li>• This is what FDEs do: <strong class="text-amber-400">turn compliance into revenue</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Key Metrics Reference -->
  <div class="mt-12 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">📊 FDE Must-Know Business Metrics</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
      <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="text-indigo-400 font-semibold text-sm">MRR</div>
        <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Monthly Recurring Revenue</div>
        <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Subscribers × ARPU</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold text-sm">Churn Rate</div>
        <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Customer loss %</div>
        <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Lost / Total customers</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm">LTV</div>
        <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Lifetime Value</div>
        <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">ARPU × Avg lifespan</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm">CAC</div>
        <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Acquisition Cost</div>
        <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Sales+Marketing / New</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm">ROI</div>
        <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Return on Investment</div>
        <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">(Gain-Cost)/Cost × 100</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Impact Report Template -->
  <div class="mt-8 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">📄 Impact Report Template (Post-Launch)</h3>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 font-mono text-sm">
      <div class="text-indigo-400">EXECUTIVE SUMMARY</div>
      <div class="text-slate-400 mt-1">Project: Checkout Optimization</div>
      <div class="text-slate-400">Duration: 4 weeks | Cost: $60,000</div>
      <div class="text-slate-400 mt-2 text-green-400">RESULTS: Abandonment 15% → 4.2% (72% reduction)</div>
      <div class="text-slate-400">Revenue recovered: $156K/month = $1.87M/year</div>
      <div class="text-slate-400">ROI: 31x | NPS: +22 points</div>
      <div class="text-slate-500 mt-2">RECOMMENDATION: Phase 2 (mobile) = additional $500K/year</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
